        "prompt": "Use case: photorealistic-natural\nAsset type: Morphous transparent motif cutout source\nPrimary request: Create only a duckweed mat botanical motif for a design-system catalog, isolated as one complete floating plant cluster on a removable chroma-key background.\nSubject: An overhead irregular mat of tiny duckweed fronds, many small round and oval lime-green leaves with natural size variation, fresh yellow-green highlights, subtle darker green undersides, and a few dark teal still-pond water gaps visible inside the mat. Botanical accuracy for duckweed, lightweight floating texture, crisp leaf edges, compact organic silhouette.\nComposition/framing: centered complete cutout with generous padding; include the full irregular mat edge without cropping. Clean even studio lighting, no cast shadow, no contact shadow.\nTransparent workflow: place the subject on a perfectly flat solid #ff00ff chroma-key background for removal. The background must be one uniform color with no shadows, gradients, texture, reflections, floor plane, or lighting variation. Do not use #ff00ff anywhere in the subject.\nConstraints: no lotus, no lily pads, no algae slime, no flowers, no insects, no fish, no pond landscape outside the mat, no container, no hand, no props, no second subject, no text, no watermark, no reflection."
