        "prompt": "Use case: photorealistic-natural\nAsset type: Morphous transparent motif cutout source\nPrimary request: Create only spruce needles as an isolated complete cutout source for a design-system motif, no environment, no props, no text.\nSubject: One natural boreal spruce twig with dense radial dark green spruce needles, cool blue shadow between needles, a few cone-brown woody stem details and tiny mature cone scales tucked near the base. Accurate spruce needle form: short stiff individual needles, crisp pointed tips, slightly waxy surface, varied deep green tones, subtle boreal neutral highlights. No full tree, no forest scene, no snow, no extra plants.\nComposition/framing: centered complete cutout with generous padding on all sides; show the whole twig and needle cluster without cropping; elegant diagonal branch gesture suitable for a motif asset.\nLighting/mood: clean studio light that preserves dark green needles, blue-shadow depth, cone-brown woody texture, and crisp operational clarity.\nTransparent workflow: place the subject on a perfectly flat solid #ff00ff chroma-key background for removal. The background must be one uniform color with no shadows, gradients, texture, reflections, floor plane, or lighting variation. Do not use #ff00ff anywhere in the subject.\nConstraints: no text, no watermark, no decorative background, no cast shadow, no contact shadow, no reflection, no second separate subject, no animals, no flowers, no bright unrelated colors."
